      "span_text": "Careful immunohistochemical and ultrastructural studies of the choroidal vasculature, Bruch's membrane and RPE in animals with each of these treatment regimens and genotypes, such as those used previously to evaluate the effects of cigarette smoke on the RPE-choroid complex, [CITATION_1] are especially warranted."
